  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>red wine vinegar</strong>, 2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water</strong> to a bowl</p><p>Peel and slice <strong>half </strong>your <strong>red onion[s]</strong> as thinly as you can, then add to the bowl and set aside to pickle – this is your <strong>quick-pickled onion</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/766.step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/766.step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/766.step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/766.step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/766.step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain and rinse your <strong>black beans</strong></p><p>Heat a pot with a lid with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat and once hot, add your <strong>ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika </strong>and cook for 10-20 secs or until fragrant</p><p>Add the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>black beans, soy sauce</strong> and 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[225ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml]</span> <strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water</strong> and season with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Cook, covered, for 10 min or until the beans are very soft</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/766__.step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/766__.step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/766__.step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/766__.step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/766__.step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, finely dice the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>red onion </strong>and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Zest (try to grate lightly with a micro-plane or sharp box grater and avoid grating the white pith, as this is very bitter!) and juice the <strong>lime[s]</strong></p><p>Core and slice the <strong>apple[s]</strong> into matchsticks</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/766.step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/766.step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/766.step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/766.step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/766.step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced onion </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> </strong>cook over a medium heat for 3-4 min or until softened</p><p>Add your <strong>chipotle paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and <strong>pork mince </strong>(remove the paper if required!), breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p><p>Season with<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for 7-8 min until the pork is crispy and cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/766.step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/766.step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/766.step-4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/766.step-4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/766.step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the pork mince is cooking, combine the <strong>apple matchsticks </strong>with the <strong>lime juice</strong>, <strong>lime zest </strong>and <strong>mayo </strong>in a small bowl – this is your <strong>zesty</strong> <strong>apple</strong> <strong>slaw</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/766.step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/766.step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
