          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/766.step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the black beans have softened, add a very large knob of <strong>butter</strong> to the pot and mash them to a coarse paste – these are your <strong>refried beans</strong></p><p>Drain the <strong>quick-pickled onion</strong>, discard the liquid</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/766__.step-7-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/766__.step-7-x400.jpg",
