          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/766__.step-7-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/766__.step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Layer up the <strong>warmed tortillas</strong> with the <strong>pork </strong>and <strong>refried beans</strong></p><p>Garnish the <strong>assembled tacos</strong> with the<strong> zesty apple slaw</strong> and <strong>quick-pickled onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
